{"tid":233173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔港女狙擊橫洲UGL 港奸689敗走","createTime":"2017-05-07T11:03:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-07T12:37:39.000Z","uid":13663,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e47f32655e27315dc49f38a6589dc65e5ea97b83","tid":233173,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:03:38.000Z","msg":"任期尚餘不足2個月的特首梁振英，早前批評反對派示威阻他落區，惟近日頻頻上載落區相片和短片，鏡頭裡完全掃去反對聲音，只見不少中老年人向他索合照。梁特是日到訪大埔，民建聯北區區議員劉國勳亦陪同在側，梁雖同樣獲不少中老年人索合照，但亦遇上一名烈女痛罵，但全程以笑遮醜。<br />\n<br />\n網民Rocena Lee Yan Yan上載她狙擊梁特的2段片段，不滿「689仆街落大埔扮落區親民，#家陣就畀你聽下民意呀仆街」。她連珠炮發向梁特追問橫洲、TSA和收受UGL 5,000萬元風波，並要求對方向全港人道歉，但梁全程未有理會，一直微笑。<br />\n<br />\n她又指梁特身邊「全部係警察同戲子，圍威喂扮落區！」並報稱有疑似女警阻檔著其鏡頭，另一名桃紅色衫大叔則拍攝和挑釁她，「仲有一班戲子喺附近同佢影相，話支持佢」，慨嘆「呢種就係#共產黨式落區&hellip;&hellip;#主流傳媒唔會報嘅民意」。<br />\n<br />\n【網民點睇】<br />\nIris Au：嘩&hellip;&hellip;好精彩，向鬧689的精英致敬！<br />\nAmy Lee：好嘢，全部都是我哋想鬧嘅嘢，謝謝妳<br />\nWM Pang：女中豪傑<br />\nPaul Kwok：689，你係咪好想聽直接民意嘅？這便是直接民意了！<br />\nYee Chung：你真係好叻，仲要埋到身係咁X"},{"pid":"cb4b6dfc6ddcc8dcb8443a611e999311d5321532","tid":233173,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:04:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170507&amp;guid=56662268&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170507%26guid%3D56662268%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=bfe02299\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170507%26guid%3D56662268%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=74fcd01f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170507&amp;guid=56662268&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"2bb994f8071a90d671eb214c07888f03bcf58502","tid":233173,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T11:07:00.000Z","msg":"希望義士唔好俾藍絲搞"},{"pid":"a5500b9d3cc48f58f6889645c147699c8359c73e","tid":233173,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-07T12:37:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}